raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Rise and shine!! ☀️
Mabel: Good morning sleepyhead!
Player: Morning!
Player: You're up early
Mabel: I never really fell asleep 😅
Player: Oh no
Player: How bad was it?
Mabel: Let's just say Mr Buttons and I had a lot of quality time staring at the ceiling
Player: Awwh no, that's rough
Player: First nights are always the worst but it'll get better
Mabel: Hope so 😔
Mabel: What about you?
Mabel: How did you sleep?
Player: Not great either honestly
Player: My back isn't too happy with me
Mabel: Thought: I'd massage your poor little back every morning
Mabel: That's it
Mabel: I have to turn this block of cement into my pillow kingdom 😤
Mabel: So if you ever want to come over and relax here
Mabel: I'll have a comfy bed for you to rest on 🥰
Mabel: What do you think?
- I'd love to! [#love]
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
	Player: I'd love to!
	Mabel: Yay hehe
	Mabel: This bed is gonna officially going to be the princess' quarters
	Mabel: And only her loyal subject is allowed to take naps from time to time 😌
- Are you okay with us being that close? [#lust]
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: Are you okay with us being that close?
	Mabel: O-of course I am 😳
	Mabel: Thought: The bed IS kinda small...
	Mabel: Thought: You might feel how warm I am 
Mabel: But hopefully the noise won't bother you
Player: Oh was it noisy too?
Mabel: There was a group outside my window that kept laughing out loud at like 2am
Player: Looks like people are already starting their parties and hangouts
Mabel: Also I could hear the guy who lives next to me talking on the phone all night 😅
Mabel: The wall is more like a piece of cardboard in between us
Mabel: Thought: He said some pretty weird stuff too
Player: Yeah there was some drinking in my dorm too
Mabel: Already?? 😳
Player: Yeah
Player: Welcome to college lol
Mabel: Thought: Drunk people are so scary
Mabel: I don't think I could ever do that
Mabel: Like just... hang out like that
Mabel: Is that weird?
- Not weird at all [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: Not weird at all
	Player: You do you
	Mabel: 😊
	Mabel: Thanks
- You might warm up to it
	Player: You might warm up to it
	Player: College changes people
	Mabel: Maybe but I don't wanna change to doing that stuff 😝
	Mabel: Could you do stuff like that?
	- I don't think so
		Player: I don't think so
		Mabel: Then why do you think I'd change 😂
		Player: Idk! Who knows 😆
	- I might have it in me [#distrust]
		set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
		Player: I might have it in me
		Mabel: Wow my boyfriend is a party animal 🥹
		Mabel: Just don't come home too late okay?
		- Of course
			Player: Of course
			Player: I'll be responsible about it haha
			Mabel: If you say so 🙂
		- No promises 😝 [#distrust]
			set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
			Player: No promises 😝
			Mabel: 😕
Mabel: Also it looks like hot water in the showers don't last too long 🙃
Player: Learned that the hard way? 😄
Mabel: I may have screamed a lil...
Mabel: At 7am 😶
Mabel: Everyone probably thinks I'm insane now
Player: Amazing first impression 😂
Mabel: I KNOW 😭
Mabel: Some girl knocked on the stall to check if I was okay
Mabel: I said I was fine
Mabel: I was not fine...
Mabel: The water was SO cold 🥶
Player: That's hilarious
Player: I wish I could've seen your face
Mabel: You would've laughed at me 😤
Player: Absolutely ❤️
Mabel: RUDE
Mabel: But fair 😂
do social_post(\"erika_intro\")
Mabel: So what are you up to today?
Player: Still not finished unpacking
Player: But maybe I'll go for a walk and check out the campus
Mabel: Same here
Mabel: I have SO many boxes left
Mabel: Mom srsly went overboard
Mabel: I found three packs of batteries??
Mabel: For what?? I don't even have anything that uses batteries 🥹
Player: Emergency supply
Mabel: For WHAT emergency
Player: You never know
Mabel: 😂
Mabel: Okay I should actually start unpacking
Mabel: Instead of just talking about unpacking
Mabel: img: mabel/10
Mabel: Hehe
Player: Novel concept
Mabel: I know right
Mabel: Mabel, at your service!
Mabel: Talk soon?
Player: Always
Mabel: 😊
Mabel: Okay bye!!
Mabel: Mabel007 mission commence!
Player: Good luck agent
Mabel: 😂❤️
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
